        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Sustainable Investment Policies Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill requires investment advisers to establish and follow a sustainable investment policy, including policies relating to the corporate governance practices, labor and human rights practices, and the environmental risks of the entities receiving investments. </p>]]>
        </text>
